<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>According to existing documentation getMessages() method returns a list of validation failure messages as  =&gt;  pairs.</p>

<p>It's declared, that getErrors() value can be also get calling array_keys() on the return value from getMessages().</p>

<p>But different validators in the validator chain may have the same message keys, so some messages may be lost.</p>

<p>It also produces problems in Zend_Filter_Input, which uses validators conception for messages processing. All rule validation errors messages are stored within one array.</p>

